00:41:09.450 --> 00:41:11.485
And I just told you that I love you.

00:41:12.090 --> 00:41:13.185
Right now!

00:41:16.460 --> 00:41:19.025
But... and you really
can't see the difference?

00:41:19.030 --> 00:41:22.355
So what, you just want me
to... say it back?

