No.

00:41:23.400 --> 00:41:25.565
No, I want you to stop
trying to fuck me,

00:41:25.970 --> 00:41:28.135
and I want you to stop
throwing fuckin' chairs

00:41:28.140 --> 00:41:29.400
out the fuckin' window!

